Class NullExecutor

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.iu.dsc.tws.executor.threading.NullExecutor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IExecution

    public class NullExecutor
extends java.lang.Object
implements IExecution
    If task count is lesser than no. of workers, that worker will remain idle. This executor will be returned to the user in such cases, since twister2 doesn't expect users to handle such cases manually.
